    <narrativeNotes>The Leaper was a simple human being that underwent extreme mutations into a bioweapon at the hands of VOID. When deployed against their foes, the Leaper successfully killed a powerful Psycaster, but in doing so, part of their powers and psyche were transfered to the Leaper, but also caused it to fall into the Backrooms. Now with their humanity returned, the Leaper rejected violence, and refused to be a simple bioweapon, instead taking on the role of colony chef, but stepped up to save the day when needed.</narrativeNotes>
